Package: libuhttpmock
Section: libs
Architecture: ARCH
Priority: optional
Provides: uhttpmock (= ${binary:Version}) 
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: a library for mocking web service APIs which use HTTP or HTTPS.  
 This package provides libuhttpmock, a shared library 
 which implements recording and playback of HTTP 
 request-response traces.

Package: libuhttpmock-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: ARCH
Priority: optional
Provides: uhttpmock-dev (= ${binary:Version}) 
Depends: libuhttpmock (= ${binary:Version}), 
 glib2-dev, libsoup-dev 
Description: uhttpmock headers and static library
 This package provides the libuhttpmock static library, 
 pkgconfig data and header files required to develop
 applications which use libuhttpmock API functions.
